type.description:
## Crafting Table

---


[Entity Action Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/entity_action_types/crafting_table)

Brings up the Crafting Table GUI as if the player has interacted with one.

Type ID: `origins:crafting_table`

---

### Examples

```json
"entity_action": {
    "type": "origins:crafting_table"
}
```
